{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"357dedf8e6","title":"重庆形势严重项英曾山暂勿离开军队","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4a0e5e7870","index":0,"year":1940,"month":12,"day":18,"articleId":"357dedf8e6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji15.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji15":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b1c5804423","type":"paragraph","text":"重庆形势严重项英曾山暂勿离开军队","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"357dedf8e6"},{"id":"6065955ab5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年12月18日）叶、项：甲、重庆形势严重，项曾以二人暂勿离开军队。乙、希夷及一部人员北上，望速作部署。丙、秘密文件必须烧毁，严防袭击","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"357dedf8e6"},{"id":"e67e8a3cae","type":"paragraph","text":"毛朱王","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"357dedf8e6"},{"id":"d846312e57","type":"paragraph","text":"十八日[1]1940年12月9日，蒋介石强令江南新因军全部限期本年12月31日前开到长江以北。12月10日，蒋介石又密电江南第三战区司令长官顾祝同，如江南新四军在31日以前没有道命北装，就立即消灭之。这是毛泽素和朱德、中共中央军委到主席王祥给新四军军长叶挺和副罩长项英的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"357dedf8e6"}],"page":{"id":"ded7c8229d","publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"357dedf8e6","start":280,"end":280}}}},"__N_SSG":true}